bramspr.symboltable

Class ValueYielderSymbol

  • java.lang.Object
    • bramspr.symboltable.Symbol
      • bramspr.symboltable.ValueYielderSymbol
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    FunctionSymbol, VariableSymbol

    public abstract class ValueYielderSymbol
extends Symbol
    Symbol table entries associated with entities in a Bramspr-program that yield a value, are all subclasses of this abstract class. These entities are variables (see VariableSymbol) and functions (see FunctionSymbol). The attribute they share is a return suit, so this abstract class defines that attribute. For quick access, it is also possible to request the return type and constancy directly, instead of via the suit.
